snippet.title: Sodaman Gameplay - Pepsiman PS1 Inspired Game
snippet.description: Sodaman is inpsired by the classic Playstation 1 game Pepsiman an action game where the superhero Pepsiman is saving a person who is dehydrated by giving them a can of Pepsi.
